WORLD-RENOWNED former Manchester United, Preston North End, Real Madrid, AC Milan, LA Galaxy, Paris Saint-Germain and England national team midfielder David Beckham will address the Discovery Leadership Summit at the Sandton Convention Centre in Joburg on Monday. The summit is a flagship, global thought-leadership event that promotes the sharing of intellectual capital to contribute to leadership in business, government and civil society.One of the world&rsquo;s most celebrated and recognised sportsmen, Beckham played football professionally for more than 20 years. &ldquo;I&rsquo;m pleased to be attending the Discovery Leadership Summit,&rdquo; said Beckham. &ldquo;It&rsquo;s always great returning to South Africa, where I have always felt the warmth and passionate spirit of its people.&rdquo;This year, the Discovery Leadership Summit&rsquo;s theme is &ldquo;Inspiring Minds&rdquo;.